Check the .sh file for the parts you need to change to make it work in your environment.
Run the .sh file.

What to do with the gerenated "KPOINTS_supercell.out" file:
    * Copy the number of SC-Kpts, as well as their coordinates, and
      paste them into ABINIT's ".in" file in the step #3.
        * They are not in cartesian coordinates.
